{
  "name": "Thesis & Dissertation Research Assistant",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📚 Thesis & Dissertation Research Assistant\n\n### What this workflow does\n1. Watches Google Drive folder for thesis/chapter uploads\n2. Downloads and extracts academic content\n3. Identifies thesis statement, methodology, framework\n4. Searches academic databases for related papers\n5. Compiles reading list sorted by citations\n6. Logs research summary to Google Sheets\n7. Sends Slack notification with findings\n\n### Setup steps\n1. Connect Google Drive account (OAuth2)\n2. Get PDF Vector API key from pdfvector.com/api-keys\n3. Create Google Sheet with columns:\n   Title, Chapter, Thesis Statement, Methodology, Framework, Key Concepts, Search Terms, Papers Found, Research Questions, Processed Date\n4. Update spreadsheet ID in Google Sheets node\n5. Set your thesis folder ID in Google Drive Trigger\n6. Connect Slack and set research channel\n\n### Academic databases searched\n- Semantic Scholar\n- PubMed\n- ArXiv\n\n### Perfect for\n- PhD students writing dissertations\n- Graduate researchers doing lit reviews\n- Academic writers finding related work",
        "height": 620,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "sticky-main",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -140,
        -20
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📊 Extracted Fields\n\n- Title & Author\n- Institution & Degree\n- Thesis statement\n- Key concepts\n- Methodology\n- Theoretical framework\n- Research questions\n- Keywords for search",
        "height": 220,
        "width": 200
      },
      "id": "sticky-extract",
      "name": "Sticky Note1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        480,
        -60
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔬 Academic Sources\n\n- Semantic Scholar\n- PubMed (medical)\n- ArXiv (preprints)\n\nReturns top 15 papers\nsorted by citation count",
        "height": 180,
        "width": 200
      },
      "id": "sticky-sources",
      "name": "Sticky Note2",
