        "text": "=📚 *Thesis Research Summary*\n\n*Document:* {{ $('Compile Research').item.json.fileName }}\n*Title:* {{ $('Compile Research').item.json.title }}\n*Chapter:* {{ $('Compile Research').item.json.chapterTitle }}\n\n---\n\n📝 *Thesis Statement:*\n{{ $('Compile Research').item.json.thesisStatement }}\n\n🔬 *Methodology:* {{ $('Compile Research').item.json.methodology }}\n📐 *Framework:* {{ $('Compile Research').item.json.theoreticalFramework }}\n\n---\n\n🔑 *Key Concepts:*\n{{ $('Compile Research').item.json.keyConcepts }}\n\n❓ *Research Questions:*\n{{ $('Compile Research').item.json.researchQuestions }}\n\n---\n\n📖 *Top Related Papers ({{ $('Compile Research').item.json.paperCount }} found):*\n{{ $('Compile Research').item.json.readingList }}\n\n---\n\n🔗 Document: https://drive.google.com/file/d/{{ $('Compile Research').item.json.fileId }}",
